---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - Blicksel Picks" description="Learn about our mission to provide honest, detailed Amazon product reviews">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About Blicksel Picks</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
        Your trusted source for honest Amazon product reviews and recommendations
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          At Blicksel Picks, we believe that making informed purchasing decisions shouldn't be overwhelming. 
          With thousands of products available on Amazon, finding the right one for your needs can be challenging. 
          That's where we come in.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Our team of experienced reviewers thoroughly tests and evaluates products across various categories, 
          from electronics and home appliances to health and fitness gear. We provide honest, unbiased reviews 
          that help you understand the real-world performance of products before you buy.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What We Do</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Hands-on Testing:</strong> We personally test every product we review, putting them through real-world scenarios.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Comprehensive Comparisons:</strong> We compare similar products to help you find the best value for your money.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Buying Guides:</strong> We create detailed guides to help you understand what features matter most.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Regular Updates:</strong> We keep our reviews current with the latest product versions and market changes.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Review Process</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Research</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We research the market and identify the most promising products to test.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Test</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We conduct thorough testing over several weeks to evaluate performance.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Review</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We write detailed, honest reviews highlighting both pros and cons.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Transparency & Trust</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We believe in complete transparency with our readers. As an Amazon Associate, we earn from qualifying purchases 
          when you use our affiliate links. This commission helps us maintain our website and continue providing free, 
          high-quality content.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          However, our affiliate relationships never influence our reviews. We maintain editorial independence and only 
          recommend products we genuinely believe offer value to our readers. If a product doesn't meet our standards, 
          we'll tell you honestly, regardless of any potential commission.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 {
    @apply text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4;
  }
  
  .prose p {
    @apply mb-4 text-gray-700;
  }
</style>
</Layout>
